On the basis of a presentation, the regional dean Georg Schmitt explained the new guidelines for pastoral care units in the Archdiocese of Freiburg.
Accordingly, SE Haslach as a congregation will in future form a corporation under public law, which will assume the rights and duties of the six individual church congregations to date.
There will only be a joint parish council and a board of trustees, in which the pastor is represented by virtue of his office.
From each parish at least two elected members are to be represented, in the six parishes so-called parish teams are formed locally.
