Business for Britain was launched in April with the aim of bringing the economy together and defining what those who deliver prosperity and jobs in Britain want to change about our relationship with the EU.
To this end, we commissioned the largest and most comprehensive survey of British business leaders and asked them what they thought of Britain, the economy and the EU.
YouGov surveyed more than 1,000 business leaders, covering roughly the size, sectors and regions of British business.
